<div style="text-align: right;"><div class="page-rate-widget-box"><span class="rate-points">rating:&nbsp;<span class="number prw54353">+56</span></span><span class="rateup btn btn-default"><a title="I like it" href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.modules.PageRateWidgetModule.listeners.rate(event, 1)">+</a></span><span class="ratedown btn btn-default"><a title="I don't like it" href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.modules.PageRateWidgetModule.listeners.rate(event, -1)">&#8211;</a></span><span class="cancel btn btn-default"><a title="Cancel my vote" href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.modules.PageRateWidgetModule.listeners.cancelVote(event)">x</a></span></div></div>
<p>Hello! I'm CaimanChameleon,<br />
Welcome to my art page!<br />
I make some Low Poly-ish (for lack of a better word) of different SCPs and stuff.</p>
<p>Please do not share any of my work without crediting me and/or asking permission. My contact info is on this page and I respond quickly.</p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Why&nbsp;do&nbsp;some&nbsp;images&nbsp;have&nbsp;a&nbsp;TK&nbsp;logo&nbsp;on&nbsp;it?</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">I've&nbsp;gone&nbsp;by&nbsp;many&nbsp;names</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>I have gone by ThaumielKeter (it's my Reddit name, Don't judge) and ThaumKet but realized it was stupid and went with this name.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Why&nbsp;CaimanChameleon?</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">I&nbsp;thought&nbsp;it&nbsp;was&nbsp;clever...</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>I come from a Colombian family and was born in Florida. A caiman is a type of Alligator that is found in Colombia and there are alligators in Florida.<br />
I thought it was clever.</p>
The chameleon part is just because of my love for chameleons<br />
here a baby photo of mine <a href="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/caimanchameleon/David"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/caimanchameleon/David/medium.jpg" alt="David" class="image" /></a></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Do&nbsp;you&nbsp;do&nbsp;commissions?</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Do&nbsp;you&nbsp;do&nbsp;commissions?</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>Yeah, I do. $5 for one $8 for two. I am willing for a bargain if you need to. I can make some art for your SCP, but I don't recommend using it for an image <em>on</em> your SCP, it will look out of place</p>
<p>I'd have to read your SCP or tale, and take hours of my time to make your request.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Contact&nbsp;me</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Contact&nbsp;me</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p><a href="https://www.reddit.com/user/ThaumielKeter">https://www.reddit.com/user/ThaumielKeter</a><br />
CaimánChameleon#7929 for discord<br />
<a href="https://twitter.com/CaimanChameleon">https://twitter.com/CaimanChameleon</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p>(I'm just unloading all the art I have made, for now, there is no order)<br />
I am only using the art I <em>want</em> to share here.<br />
much of my previous work is not great. I may share them in the future or you can find it on my Reddit.<br />
Let's get to the artwork!</p>
